title: Finals Week
caption: December 13th
description: Hey everyone! Good luck on Finals :) All your hard work this semester will pay off, so just push a little harder. This week has a special schedule so refer to the announcements or Reminds pushed out for those. Thanks for everything this semester, so take care, study hard, and rest well over break. I'll see you all when we come back! :) — Kaden

title: Winter Break
caption: Dec. 6 — Jan. 3
description: Have a wonderful winter break all. Break begins on December 16th and goes until January 3rd (beginning of Winter Intercession). Take care, stay warm, and happy holidays!

title: Winter Intercession
caption: January 3rd
description: Winter Intercession begins on January 3rd, 2023. Most classes meet at UHS with the exception of Directed Studies and Ski/Snowboarding. Please check your Reminds and emails for detailed information regarding your classes. These classes are mandatory, and the time of your selected electives typically runs the length of a normal UHS day. Enjoy your electives!
